    {
      "id": "5da8cbac-1977-40c1-bf90-58029ac4eca3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Goal of paper is to predict a student’s level of mastery of math questions based on dialogue whithin the LMS. The paper uses a multi-granularity attention mechanism to capture pedagogical instructions from dialogue transcriptions.",
